Package de.presti.ree6.utils.apis

Class Notifier

java.lang.Object
de.presti.ree6.utils.apis.Notifier
public class Notifier extends Object
Utility class used for Event Notifiers. Such as Twitch Livestream, YouTube Upload or Twitter Tweet.
